@node "Require" "Requirements"
 - AmiTCP 3+ or Commodore's AS225R2 or any compatible TCP/IP stack (like INet225).
 - 2 Mb of memory free is a minimum to start Pine. If you plan to receive large
   pieces of mail or like to read binary newsgroups, more may be needed.
 - ixemul.library 43.x. It can be found on aminet in dev/gcc
 - At least Workbench 2.04 (V37). @{b}1.3 is DEAD@{ub}.
@endnode

